Description: stolon is a PostgreSQL manager for PostgreSQL high availability.
 It's cloud native because it'll let you keep an high available PostgreSQL
 inside your containers (kubernetes integration) but also on every other
 kind of infrastructure (cloud IaaS, old style infrastructures etc...)
